{% extends "user/login.html.twig" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container">
    <form id="register-form" class="jumbotron" method="post">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">
                <h1><i class="fa-rocket"></i>&nbsp;Shuttle</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-4">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control input-lg" {{ setValue('email') }} placeholder="Email" required>
                    {{ formError('email') }}
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" name="company" class="form-control input-lg" {{ setValue('company') }} placeholder="Société">
                    {{ formError('company') }}
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control input-lg" {{ setValue('password') }} placeholder="Mot de passe" required>
                    {{ formError('password') }}
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="password" name="confirm" class="form-control input-lg" {{ setValue('confirm') }} placeholder="Confirmation" required>
                    {{ formError('confirm') }}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" col-md-4">
                <h2>Créez votre compte</h2>
                <p>Sed quis elit scelerisque, porttitor velit et, porta leo. Maecenas quis adipiscing enim. In lacinia id purus porttitor vehicula. Sed pretium eros non dolor dapibus, et viverra risus feugiat. Sed iaculis commodo turpis, euismod semper quam eleifend eget.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col-sm-offset-4 col-sm-4">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-block btn-primary">je m'inscris</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col-xs-12" style="text-align: center;">
                Vous avez déjà un compte ? <a href="login" class="dynamic">Identifiez-vous</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
{% endblock %}